{
  "chapter": 74,
  "chapter_summary": "第七十四回\"人面兽心\"讲述了江玉郎在客栈中与无牙门门人的冲突。高矮两名无牙门门人跟踪江玉郎，企图威胁他交出慕容九妹并带他们去找轩辕三光、江小鱼和花无缺。江玉郎假意合作，趁二人不备将他们制服。随后，铁萍姑醒来，江玉郎用哭诉和甜言蜜语哄骗她原谅自己。此时，无牙门门主突然出现，杀死两名被辱的门人，并威胁江玉郎在七天内带他找到三人。江玉郎试图讨价还价时，门主展示了恐怖的碧色火焰武功。关键时刻，一个神秘人物狂笑着出现，声称无牙门武功算不得什么，剧情留下悬念。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位说的可是在下么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_de_na_ren",
      "speaker_name": "矮的那人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下也曾见到过不少花丛圣手、风流种子，但若论对付女人的手段，却简直没有人能比得上兄台一半的。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位说笑话的本事，倒当真妙极。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_de_na_ren",
      "speaker_name": "矮的那人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在这位姑娘，已是兄台的手中之物了，眼见兄台立刻便要软玉温香抱个满怀，兄台难道就不愿让我兄弟也开开心么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_de_na_ren",
      "speaker_name": "高的那人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下只是说，兄台若想真个销魂，多少也要给我兄弟一些好处，否则……",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位难道也想分一杯羹么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_de_na_ren",
      "speaker_name": "矮的那人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这倒不敢，只是兄台既有了新人，棉被里那位姑娘，总该让给我兄弟了吧？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来两位知道的还不少。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_de_na_ren",
      "speaker_name": "高的那人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老实说，自从兄台开始盯上这位姑娘时，一举一动，我兄弟都瞧得清清楚楚。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "妙极妙极，想不到兄台倒是对在下如此有兴趣，快请先坐下来，容在下敬两位一杯。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_de_na_ren",
      "speaker_name": "高的那人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "酒，可以打扰，下酒物我兄弟自己随身带着。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来阁下乃是和那五位朋友一路的，这就难怪对在下如此清楚了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_de_na_ren",
      "speaker_name": "高的那人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下等除了要请兄台将慕容家的姑娘割爱之外，还要向兄台打听一件事。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_de_na_ren",
      "speaker_name": "高的那人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "洞里的那三个人，究竟是些什么人？和你又有什么关系？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那三人一个叫轩辕三光，一个叫江小鱼，一个叫花无缺。两位方才既然瞧见了，总该知道他们都是在下的仇人吧？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_de_na_ren",
      "speaker_name": "高的那人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "很好，好极了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "方才那五位朋友，难道已被他们……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_de_na_ren",
      "speaker_name": "高的那人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，已被他们杀了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如此说来，在下与两位正是同仇敌忾，在下理当敬两位一杯。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_de_na_ren",
      "speaker_name": "高的那人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "很好，兄台喝了这杯酒，就跟我兄弟走吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_de_na_ren",
      "speaker_name": "矮的那人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "至于这位姑娘，兄台尽可在路上……哈哈，我兄弟必定为兄台准备辆又舒服、又宽敞的车子。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位要在下到哪里去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_de_na_ren",
      "speaker_name": "高的那人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我兄弟就想请兄台劳驾一趟，随我兄弟一同回去，好将那三人诱来。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位意思，在下已全部了解，两位既是想将三人诱去复仇的，岂非也与在下有利，在下又怎会不答应？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ai_de_na_ren",
      "speaker_name": "矮的那人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "兄台果然是个通达事理的人，在下也理当敬兄台一杯。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就凭你们两人也想将我带走，你们还差得远哩！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道我做错了，我知道我对不起你，只求你原谅我……",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……我恨不得……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你若恨我，就杀了我吧！我……我实在控制不住自己，我也醉了，我们本不该喝酒的。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "求你杀了我吧！你杀了我，也许我还好受些。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我做的虽不对，但我心却是真诚的，只要你相信我，我会证明给你看，我这一辈子都不会令你失望的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你要么就原谅我，要么就杀了我吧……你可以杀死我，但却不能要我不喜欢你，我死也要喜欢你……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不恨我了？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只要你说的是真的，只要你莫忘记今天的话，我……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_mi_ren_wu",
      "speaker_name": "神秘人物",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是你点了这两人的穴道？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是在下，在下本不知要拿他们怎么办，阁下此番解决了他们，在下简直不知该如何感激才好。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_mi_ren_wu",
      "speaker_name": "神秘人物",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我就是他们的主人！他们本是我的奴隶！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但你……杀死他们的，并不是我。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这……这是什么意思，我不懂。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_mi_ren_wu",
      "speaker_name": "神秘人物",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这两人既已被你所辱，我只有杀了他们，免得他们再为我丢人现眼。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有时我也杀人的，但我总是要有一个十分好的理由，譬如说……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_mi_ren_wu",
      "speaker_name": "神秘人物",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "譬如说什么？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "譬如说，当我知道一个人要杀我的时候，我通常会先杀了他。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_mi_ren_wu",
      "speaker_name": "神秘人物",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我要杀人时，就不跟他多话的。",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你为何不想杀我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_mi_ren_wu",
      "speaker_name": "神秘人物",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你若能在七天之内，带我找到轩辕三光、江小鱼和花无缺，你不但现在不会死，而且还会长命得很！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们也是我的仇人，你若能杀得了他们，我自然很愿意带你去找他们，只可惜要杀这三个人，并不是件容易事，被他们杀，倒容易得很。你若杀不成他们，反被他们杀死，我岂非也要被你连累。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_mi_ren_wu",
      "speaker_name": "神秘人物",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你要怎样才相信我能杀得了他们？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这就要看你有什么法子能令我相信了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_mi_ren_wu",
      "speaker_name": "神秘人物",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我何止有一千种法子可以令你相信，你若想见识见识无牙门下的神功，我不妨先让你瞧一种……",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_mi_ren_wu",
      "speaker_name": "神秘人物",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你还想见识别的么？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_chu_xian_de_ren",
      "speaker_name": "新出现的人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无牙门下的神功，我看来却算不得什么。",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 74,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    }
  ],
